# Enabled Spectra review personas — one slug per line (a slug is the persona's
# filename without .md). A persona file in personas/ that isn't listed here is
# available but off; turn it on with /spectra-persona-enable, off with /spectra-persona-disable.
# This file is developer-owned: spectra-install seeds it only if absent and
# spectra-update never overwrites it, so your choices survive updates.
# Shipped default = the four core personas.
engineer
tester
architect
security
